{"clientId":"bot_74298","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:cee87909e7359985b3250f87e3360eb0","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"The Department of Government Enablement (DGE) is a centralized government entity in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates, dedicated to enhancing public services and supporting government entities, citizens, and residents. It's a key player in Abu Dhabis growth strategy, focusing on several key initiatives such as GovTalent, GovAcademy, GovProcurement, and TAMM.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1742278278819},"_id":"1uUCily2nXlMzup4"}
