{"clientId":"bot_74298","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:cee87909e7359985b3250f87e3360eb0","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"The Abu Dhabi Police GHQ services include:\n\n1. Traffic Profiles: Registered users can view their traffic profiles, update their address details, and perform transactional services like paying fines.\n2. Drivers Services: Registered users can view their driving licenses, renew their licenses, and perform services like issuing a replacement for a lost or damaged license, or canceling a driving trainer permit.\n3. Vehicles Services: Registered users can view their registered vehicles, view their vehicle certificates, and perform services like issuing a temporary driving permit, canceling a driving trainer permit, or adding or removing categories from their driving licenses.\n4. Public Services: This section includes services like inquiry and payment for traffic fines, retrieving traffic violations, and transferring traffic violations to the court.\n\nThese services are available to registered users who have a valid Emirates ID card and an active traffic file in the Federal Traffic and Licensing System.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1741710075990},"_id":"2CcSLU0GOOpTMHrH"}
