{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Example</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            margin: 20px;\n        }\n        .card {\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            padding: 20px;\n            width: 300px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        p {\n            color: #666;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300\" alt=\"Image Description\">\n        <h1>Card Title</h1>\n        <p>Description of the Card</p>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\nThis HTML and CSS code creates a simple card with an image, a title, and a description. The card is styled using CSS to make it visually appealing.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1739199441911},"_id":"9nVIyaH1AJJVoRlN"}
{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"SIBF stands for Sharjah International Book Fair. It's an annual international book fair held annually in Sharjah, United Arab Emirates. The fair aims to promote reading and literature globally, featuring thousands of books and other publications. It serves as a platform for authors, publishers, and industry professionals to connect and collaborate. The fair covers various aspects including book displays, panels, workshops, exhibitions, and educational programs aimed at enhancing literacy and fostering creativity among readers.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738851989204},"_id":"9oKSBsQwNQLH9UHG"}
