{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"Yes, Liferay is an open-source digital experience platform (DXP). It was developed by Alibaba Cloud and released under the Apache License 2.0, which is a permissive license that allows anyone to use, modify, and distribute the software as long as they comply with certain terms. This licensing model encourages contributions from the community and promotes transparency about the project's codebase.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738743577089},"_id":"A10fTzThBZ5pS6NM"}
{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"The context is: 'Q who established(SIBF)?AH.H. Sheikh Dr. Sultan Bin Mohammed Al QasimiQ what is(SIBF)?ASharjah International Book FairSharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) was established in 1982 by H.H. Sheikh Dr. Sultan Bin Mohammed Al Qasimi, a Member of the Supreme Council and the Ruler of Sharjah. He founded it to bring to life his vision of creating a nation of readers.The rich legacy of the SIBF has extended across four decades. It promotes both cultural and intellectual growth and exchange worldwide.The Sharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) has crossed 50 million in sales. Its a 12day cultural and literary event where book lovers can browse through millions of books and buy them at great prices. The fair also connects authors and publishers from all over the globe and facilitates meetings to discuss current trends and potential opportunities to work together. In 2023 15 million books displayed 2,023 publishers 109 participating countries 1500 childrens activitiesSIBF has expanded its reach beyond the boundaries of Sharjah. The platform heartily welcomes every speaker and author to interact. The international presence of SIBF has allowed it to explore different literary traditions and perspectives. Today, SIBF is the third largest book fair in the world. It is the most prestigious event in the Arab world and a hub for the most exciting literary events in the region. Every year, SIBF attracts the finest global talent in publishing and related industries to the Middle East.SIBF has also initiated various paths for its readers. These include educational initiatives, the Publishers Conference, Emirati Book Awards (Emirati Novel Award, Best Emirati Creative Literature Book, Best Emirati Academic Book, and Best Emirati First Novel Award), Best Arabic Novel Award, and Best International Book Awards (Best International Non-Fiction book, Best International Fiction book, and Best International First Novel Award). These initiatives have inspired many learners and led to innovation in publishing and related industries.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738532994840},"_id":"A2reaZOxZhPzTiyn"}
