{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"Certainly! Below is a simple HTML template for a card with the specified layout:\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card with Image</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f9;\n        }\n        .card {\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            max-width: 300px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .card h1 {\n            color: #333;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .card p {\n            color: #666;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin: 10px 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300\" alt=\"Image Description\">\n        <h1>Card Title</h1>\n        <p>This is a brief description of what the card contains.</p>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### Explanation:\n- **HTML Structure**: \n  - A `div` element with the class `card` holds the entire card.\n  - An `<img>` element with the `src` attribute pointing to an image URL.\n  - A `<h1>` element containing the title.\n  - A `<p>` element containing the description.\n\n- **CSS Styling**:\n  - Basic styling for the card (`border-radius`, `box-shadow`, `max-width`, `overflow`) to make it look professional.\n  - `.card img` sets the image size and position.\n  - `.card h1` centers the heading.\n  - `.card p` adds some spacing around the paragraph content.\n\nReplace `\"https://via.placeholder.com/300\"` with your actual placeholder image URL if needed. This template should work well for displaying cards with images and descriptions.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1739198676307},"_id":"AH36iRM7FPUVw79n"}
