{"clientId":"bot_39379","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:ce225013119bade54458f77722df8404","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"Liferay is a powerful opensource Digital Experience Platform (DXP) that helps organizations create, manage, and deliver personalized digital experiences across web, mobile, and connected devices. It's built on modern, flexible architecture and enables enterprises to create custom web applications and connect with backend systems and APIs.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1747339689118},"_id":"DdNX25iARAK86F36"}
