{"clientId":"67781","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:47562b2770187dd8d00a8aebf2cee48e","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:4d4a0759c90685ef504d84dea921b370","message":"test","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1742505088258},"_id":"IdSNsEPwCzIR0XFU"}
{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Example</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            color: #333;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .card {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 300px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .card h2 {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/350x150\" alt=\"Image Description\" class=\"card-image\">\n        <h2 class=\"card-header\">Card Header</h2>\n        <p class=\"card-description\">This is the description for this card.</p>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### Explanation:\n- **HTML (`index.html`)**:\n  - The `div` element with the class `card` contains the entire card.\n  - Inside the card, there's an `<img>` element to display an image.\n  - There's a `<h2>` element with the class `card-header` to display the header text.\n  - Finally, there's a `<p>` element with the class `card-description` to display the description.\n\n- **CSS (`styles.css`)**:\n  - The `.card` class styles the entire card, including its dimensions, background color, shadow, and border radius.\n  - The `.card img` class sets the image size and aspect ratio.\n  - The `.card h2` class adds some basic styling for the header text.\n  - The `.card p` class adds some basic styling for the description text.\n\nThis HTML and CSS code will generate a card with an image, a header, and a description.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1739199289791},"_id":"IdfiwuZwDgjiUICF"}
