{"clientId":"bot_74298","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:cee87909e7359985b3250f87e3360eb0","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"1. GovTalent: A program aimed at developing leadership skills and creating productive work environments within Abu Dhabis government departments.\n\n2. GovAcademy: A platform providing training and development programs to enhance the skills and knowledge of government employees.\n\n3. GovProcurement: A program designed to optimize procurement processes within Abu Dhabis government entities, supporting the local economy and fostering a strong digital foundation.\n\n4. TAMM: A unified omnichannel government ecosystem offering a wide range of services provided by the Government of Abu Dhabi, combining human interaction with technology-led solutions across various channels and facilities.\n\n5. Mawaheb: A career-driven and responsive employment support center in Abu Dhabi, preparing job seekers for current and future opportunities in the UAEs labor market.\n\n6. DGE's initiatives with Microsoft AI Tour in Dubai: A keynote address highlighting the transformative capabilities of the DGE's TAMM platform and its commitment to leveraging AI to enhance public services.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1742166219507},"_id":"Vm6zKaoCSYSmzM76"}
