{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","message":"sdad","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738449224746},"_id":"YypLQs3s2PrgzUdZ"}
{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"context: 'Q whoestablished(SIBF)?ASharjah International Book FairSharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) was established in 1982 by H.H. Sheikh Dr. Sultan Bin Mohammed Al QasimiQ what is(SIBF)?ASharjah International Book FairSharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) was established in 1982 by H.H. Sheikh Dr. Sultan Bin Mohammed Al Qasimi, a Member of the Supreme Council and the Ruler of Sharjah. He founded it to bring to life his vision of creating a nation of readers.The rich legacy of the SIBF has extended across four decades. It promotes both cultural and intellectual growth and exchange worldwide.The Sharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) has crossed 50 million in sales. Its a 12day cultural and literary event where book lovers can browse through millions of books and buy them at great prices. The fair also connects authors and publishers from all over the globe and facilitates meetings to discuss current trends and potential opportunities to work together. In 2023 15 million books displayed 2,023 publishers 109 participating countries 1500 childrens activitiesSIBF has expanded its reach beyond the boundaries of Sharjah. The platform heartily welcomes every speaker and author to interact. The international presence of SIBF has allowed it to explore different literary traditions and perspectives.Today, SIBF is the thirdlargest book fair in the world. It is the most prestigious event in the Arab world and a hub for the most exciting literary events in the region. Every year, SIBF attracts the finest global talent in publishing and related industries to the Middle East.Sharjah International Book Fair has been awarded membership to various international organizations such as the AfroAsian Publishers Association and GCC Book Committee and has been recognized by the International Publishers Association.In a dynamic environment that converges various voices in one place, SIBF offers various opportunities, captivating events, and activities such as author signings, noteworthy panel discussions, knowledgeable workshops, and exhibition sessions.SIBF has also initiated various paths for its readers. These include educational initiatives, the Publishers Conference, Emirati Book Awards (Emirati Novel Award, Best Emirati Creative Literature Book, Best","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738679051122},"_id":"YzAjAw3lvmPRl7H6"}
{"clientId":"20122","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:5d3a5dcc9ccc59fd007494179a44a949","message":"hello","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738532694749},"_id":"Z44Lz4mRUG5Ftpcb"}
{"clientId":"20122","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","message":"asd","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738532557592},"_id":"Z6a12sdA4TEz9ZOJ"}
{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"context: 'Q whoestablished(SIBF)?AH.H. Sheikh Dr. Sultan Bin Mohammed Al QasimiQ what is(SIBF)?ASharjah International Book FairSharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) was established in 1982 by H.H. Sheikh Dr. Sultan Bin Mohammed Al Qasimi, a Member of the Supreme Council and the Ruler of Sharjah. He founded it to bring to life his vision of creating a nation of readers.The rich legacy of the SIBF has extended across four decades. It promotes both cultural and intellectual growth and exchange worldwide.The Sharjah International Book Fair (SIBF) has crossed 50 million in sales. Its a 12day cultural and literary event where book lovers can browse through millions of books and buy them at great prices. The fair also connects authors and publishers from all over the globe and facilitates meetings to discuss current trends and potential opportunities to work together. In 2023 15 million books displayed 2,023 publishers 109 participating countries 1500 childrens activitiesSIBF has expanded its reach beyond the boundaries of Sharjah. The platform heartily welcomes every speaker and author to interact. The international presence of SIBF has allowed it to explore different literary traditions and perspectives.Today, SIBF is the thirdlargest book fair in the world. It is the most prestigious event in the Arab world and a hub for the most exciting literary events in the region. Every year, SIBF attracts the finest global talent in publishing and related industries to the Middle East.Sharjah International Book Fair has been awarded membership to various international organizations such as the AfroAsian Publishers Association and GCC Book Committee and has been recognized by the International Publishers Association.In a dynamic environment that converges various voices in one place, SIBF offers various opportunities, captivating events, and activities such as author signings, noteworthy panel discussions, knowledgeable workshops, and exhibition sessions.SIBF has also initiated various paths for its readers. These include educational initiatives, the Publishers Conference, Emirati Book Awards (Emirati Novel Award, Best Emirati Creative Literature Book, Best Emirati Academic Book, and Best Emirati First Novel Award), Best Arabic Novel Award, and Best International Book Awards (Best International NonFiction book, Best International Fiction book, and Best International First Novel Award). These initiatives have inspired many learners and led to innovation in publishing and related industries. d'","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738678787361},"_id":"Z87gqoHbCTnVmZHo"}
{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"Liferay helps organizations achieve several benefits by providing a comprehensive set of features and functionalities tailored specifically to digital transformation and enterprise needs. Here are some key areas where Liferay contributes to organizational success:\n\n1. **Website Development and Maintenance**:\n   - **Website Creation**: Liferay allows businesses to quickly and easily create and maintain websites, whether they're for internal use or external-facing.\n   - **Content Management**: The CMS ensures that all content is managed centrally, reducing manual effort and improving consistency.\n   - **User Management**: Role-based access controls ensure that users have appropriate permissions to access and modify content.\n\n2. **Enhanced Security**:\n   - **Integrations**: Integrating with various third-party systems enhances security by connecting different components seamlessly.\n   - **Data Protection**: Advanced security features protect sensitive information, ensuring compliance with regulations and protecting user data.\n\n3. **Customization and Flexibility**:\n   - **Modular Architecture**: The modular nature of Liferay allows for easy customization and extension, enabling businesses to tailor the platform to meet specific business requirements.\n   - **Customizable Features**: Extending the platform with custom modules and plugins adds value by offering new functionalities not available in the standard version.\n\n4. **Scalability and Performance**:\n   - **High Scalability**: Designed to handle large volumes of traffic and data, Liferay ensures that the platform remains responsive and performs well under heavy load.\n   - **Performance Optimization**: Built-in optimization techniques help in optimizing the performance of the platform, especially during peak usage periods.\n\n5. **Ease of Use and Integration**:\n   - **Extensible Framework**: The open-source community makes Liferay accessible to developers, facilitating the creation of custom solutions.\n   - **Integration Capabilities**: Seamless integration with various third-party systems and third-party applications enhances the overall productivity of the organization.\n\n6. **Customer Portal and Employee Intranet**:\n   - **Customer Portals**: Providing a single portal for customers to access company information, products, and services.\n   - **Employee Intranets**: Facilitating communication between employees and management, helping to streamline collaboration and decision-making.\n\n7. **Self-Service Platforms**:\n   - **Web Applications**: Offering self-service portals for users to interact with the platform, simplifying administrative tasks and increasing operational efficiency.\n   - **Mobile Apps**: Supporting mobile apps, making it easier for employees to access the platform from anywhere.\n\n8. **Cloud Deployment Options**:\n   - **Cloud Services**: Leveraging cloud services provided by Liferay, businesses can benefit from cost-effective and scalable infrastructure.\n   - **On-Premise Solutions**: For those looking for a dedicated environment, Liferay also offers on-premise solutions, catering to specific business needs.\n\nIn summary, Liferay helps organizations by providing a robust, customizable, and scalable platform that supports digital transformation, enhances security, and optimizes performance. Its ability to integrate with various third-party systems and provide extensive customization options sets it apart as a valuable asset for businesses seeking to build and maintain successful digital experiences.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738743472155},"_id":"Z8mfVjpJn8ILNEzv"}
