{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"context: 'Liferay is an opensource digital experience platform (DXP) designed to help businesses build web portals, intranets, and other enterprise solutions. It provides a flexible and scalable framework for creating digital experiences, enabling organizations to manage content, users, and applications efficiently.Liferays key features include a robust content management system (CMS), user management, rolebased access control, workflow automation, and integration capabilities with various thirdparty systems. It supports headless CMS functionality, allowing developers to build modern web applications using APIs while leveraging Liferay's backend services.One of Liferay's strengths is its modular architecture, which enables customization through extensions and plugins. It is widely used in industries such as finance, healthcare, government, and education for building customer portals, employee intranets, and selfservice platforms.Liferay offers both an opensource Community Edition (CE) and a commercial Enterprise Edition (EE), which includes additional features like enterprise support, security enhancements, and cloud deployment options.With its powerful tools for digital transformation, Liferay helps organizations create seamless, personalized experiences while maintaining security, scalability, and flexibility.'","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738743229122},"_id":"ZQzFdGjc0iozhW3k"}
