{"clientId":"bot_55389","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:13a402f55c5598575ac91b5fdc621ac6","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"SIFB stands for Sharjah International Book Fair. It's a big event where people can buy and read books from all over the world. It's like a big bookstore, but instead of books, it's a big event with lots of people and lots of books.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738531977093},"_id":"eXLNVJHJx7vAXfRM"}
{"clientId":"bot_74298","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:cee87909e7359985b3250f87e3360eb0","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"GovTalent is a program within the Department of Government Enablement (DGE) in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates, aimed at developing leadership skills and creating productive work environments within Abu Dhabis government departments. The program focuses on enhancing the skills and knowledge of government employees, enabling them to effectively contribute to the public sector's mission and goals.\n\nGovTalent's objectives include:\n\n1. Developing leadership skills and competencies among government employees.\n2. Enhancing the productivity and efficiency of government departments.\n3. Fostering a culture of innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning within the public sector.\n4. Supporting the recruitment and retention of top talent in Abu Dhabi's government agencies.\n\nThe program offers training and development opportunities, mentorship, and coaching to help employees grow professionally and personally, ultimately contributing to the success of Abu Dhabis government entities. By investing in its employees, the DGE aims to build a strong, capable, and innovative public sector that can effectively serve the community and drive Abu Dhabis growth and prosperity.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1742166257899},"_id":"eZVE1S684jOFyA92"}
{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"Liferay is an opensource digital experience platform (DXP) designed to help businesses build web portals, intranets, and other enterprise solutions. It provides a flexible and scalable framework for creating digital experiences, enabling organizations to manage content, users, and applications efficiently.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1738743702942},"_id":"eZYV5SGR8DHlUZ2x"}
