{"clientId":"bot_74298","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:cee87909e7359985b3250f87e3360eb0","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"The Department of Government Enablement (DGE) is a centralized government entity in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates, dedicated to enhancing public services and supporting government entities, citizens, and residents. It is a key player in Abu Dhabis growth strategy, focusing on several key initiatives such as GovTalent, GovAcademy, GovProcurement, and TAMM. The DGE aims to develop leadership skills, establish productive work environments, optimize procurement processes, and provide unified and efficient government services.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1742166432676},"_id":"f03yKO1pA48r5i5u"}
