{"clientId":"bot_ui_ai","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:f0a219b5ecf0763fe26f101c1b1d391f","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"Sure, here's a basic HTML and CSS code for a card with an image:\n\nHTML:\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n\t<title>Card Image</title>\n\t<style>\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f2f2f2;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.card {\n\t\t\twidth: 100%;\n\t\t\theight: 100%;\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\n\t\t\tborder: 0;\n\t\t\tbox-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.card img {\n\t\t\twidth: 100%;\n\t\t\theight: 100%;\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\n\t\t\tborder: 0;\n\t\t\tbox-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n\t\t}\n\t</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\t<div class=\"card\">\n\t\t<img src=\"image.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\nCSS:\n```css\nbody {\n\tfont-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n\tbackground-color: #f2f2f2;\n}\n\n.card {\n\twidth: 100%;\n\theight: 100%;\n\tmargin: 0;\n\tpadding: 0;\n\tborder: 0;\n\tbox-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n\n.card img {\n\twidth: 100%;\n\theight: 100%;\n\tmargin: 0;\n\tpadding: 0;\n\tborder: 0;\n\tbox-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n```\n\nThis code will create a basic HTML and CSS structure for a card with an image. You can customize the styles to fit your needs.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1739790088097},"_id":"g1petKBbOxgSOBcq"}
