{"clientId":"bot_54701","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:1222827d9784c14eb902377528ec606b","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:d0a00e49305c0b081e75997d3326eafb","message":"Certainly! Below is a simple HTML/CSS card that uses plain HTML and CSS without any JavaScript:\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Example</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            margin: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .card {\n            width: 300px;\n            max-width: 90%;\n            margin: auto;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n\n        .card h3 {\n            color: #333;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .card p {\n            color: #666;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .card button {\n            background-color: #007BFF;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300\" alt=\"Image Background\">\n    <h3>Card Title</h3>\n    <p>This is the content of the card.</p>\n    <button onclick=\"alert('Button clicked')\">Click Me!</button>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### Explanation:\n- **HTML Structure**: The card is wrapped within a `div` element.\n- **CSS Styling**:\n  - `.card`: Sets the dimensions, background color, shadow, padding, and styling for the card.\n  - `.card img`: Ensures the image has a maximum width of 90% and rounded corners.\n  - `.card h3`, `.card p`, and `.card button`: Styles the title, paragraph, and button respectively.\n  \nThis basic card design can be customized further based on your specific needs or requirements.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1739197931799},"_id":"qpgv64rIdHRrY38o"}
