{"clientId":"bot_74298","type":"MessageNotification","name":"Chat","data":{"from":"31323334353637383930313233343536:cee87909e7359985b3250f87e3360eb0","to":"31323334353637383930313233343536:2ff52ef52e56036e82199f8c3ddc813d","message":"The Department of Government Enablement (DGE) is a centralized government entity in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates, dedicated to enhancing public services and supporting government entities, citizens, and residents. It is a key part of Abu Dhabis government structure, focusing on several key initiatives such as GovTalent, GovAcademy, GovProcurement, and TAMM. The DGE aims to develop leadership skills, establish productive work environments, optimize procurement processes, and provide unified government services. It is a vital component of Abu Dhabis government, working to improve the quality of life for its residents through innovative and efficient public services.","chatMessageType":"Text","date":1742166461912},"_id":"uQPp5AuwwWzr02H2"}
